<item>
            <title>[LU-10765] Broken error fs handling in llapi_hsm_action_{begin,end}</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10765</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Both llapi_hsm_action_begin/end have this code in error handling:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;err_out:
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (!(hcp-&amp;gt;source_fd &amp;lt; 0))
                close(hcp-&amp;gt;source_fd);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The problem is source_fd is unsigned, so it could never be less than zero.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
